column2: SELECT   g.*,   e.*,   p.petroR9#_u,   p.petroR9#_g,   p.petroR9#_r,   p.petroR9#_i,   p.petroR9#_z,   p.petroR9#Err_u,   p.petroR9#Err_g,   p.petroR9#Err_r,   p.petroR9#Err_i,   p.petroR9#Err_z,   p.petroR5#_u,   p.petroR5#_g,   p.petroR5#_r,   p.petroR5#_i,   p.petroR5#_z,   p.petroR5#Err_u,   p.petroR5#Err_g,   p.petroR5#Err_r,   p.petroR5#Err_i,   p.petroR5#Err_z into mydb.MyTable from GalSpecInfo AS g   JOIN GalSpecExtra AS e ON g.specobjid = e.specobjid   JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS s ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid   JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON p.objid = s.objid WHERE   g.spectrotype = &&&
